items.name: ForzaTrainer
items.description: This repository hosts a versatile trainer for Forza Horizon 5, offering a range of enhancements and cheats to enrich the gaming experience. Designed for both casual players and enthusiasts, the trainer includes features such as unlimited credits, super speed, teleportation, and customizable weather conditions.

items.name: SniperElite-Trainer
items.description: This repository hosts a comprehensive trainer for the game Sniper Elite, designed to provide additional features beyond the original scope. The trainer includes functionalities such as infinite ammo, god mode, and various cheats to modify gameplay mechanics for both single-player and cooperative modes.
